{"tid":1475654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警屢反對示威申請 郭卓堅入稟覆核","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:44:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"661d7c4254cd02d0b9bf37d403e9e72028906055","tid":1475654,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190815/20749374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190815%2F20749374&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=5a729f00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190815%2F20749374&h=5472a4d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190815/20749374</a><br />\n<br />\n警屢反對示威申請 郭卓堅入稟覆核<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190815/large/1565800866_5e0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190815%2Flarge%2F1565800866_5e0a.jpg&h=c83c837d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近日警方因應「反送中」衍生的示威浪潮，多次禁止公眾遊行和集會。「覆核王」郭卓堅和（圖）退休攝影記者張德榮昨入稟申請司法覆核，指集會遊行必須獲得批准，乃違反《基本法》保障的遊行集會自由。郭在高等法院外發言指，有人會說遊行示威時常有暴動行為，然而保護市民是警察職責，而且暴動行為未必是示威者所為，「（可唔可能）你哋搵一班黑警混入嚟，嚟到做擾亂嘅嘢，然後反對晒我哋呀？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指違《基本法》<br />\n<br />\n覆核的建議答辯人為警務處處長，和公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會主席。申請書要求法庭頒令，若反對市民的遊行示威申請，便違反人權和《基本法》。郭卓堅在法院外解釋，他同意市民須知會警方擬進行遊行集會，使警方能作相應安排，只是認為警方不能反對。張德榮則強調，合法和不合法的示威是兩回事，警方一律禁止是凌駕法律，「𠵱家喺超級市場有人偷嘢，你就唔畀我去買嘢，因為有人偷嘢；呢啲完全係唔合道理嘅嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCAL2337/19<br />\n■記者勞東來  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n動保團體後日集會 轟催淚彈虐警犬"},{"pid":"731219db0d4433a65658dd3dd0d1b2f202bb6fbf","tid":1475654,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"其實呢個反對理由好on9<br />\n咁以後所有遊行都可以話因為危險所以反對<br />\n咁幾時先係安全？"},{"pid":"1210b0dc8c2b977f8185f5547ffd2adc770cdbbe","tid":1475654,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:28:00.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"f49b848fce8be72f02fa5e61ea5f0d9e22ce2655","tid":1475654,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbDbDij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbDbDij.jpg&h=e36ccd71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n612 721 805 811<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">816</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">818</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e760e760be3056e52603a506301cb55b1220ee12","tid":1475654,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"一早應該要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529298be7dfd0dd2a663a7f3679e85d35f3daa90","tid":1475654,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"覆核王出手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c624e96bacee84323e02d0066cc6c3039d1ee597","tid":1475654,"uid":45523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"好開心終於有人出手"},{"pid":"4a00678e1ad27d5e1a8e37ccf59ee4b70a913c43","tid":1475654,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：寵物集會（1930愛丁堡廣場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>8月23日</strong>：會計界遊行（1230遮打花園）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"}]}